systemData.Description: Metadata pertaining to creation and last modification of the resource.

location.Description: The location of the Template Spec. It cannot be changed after Template Spec creation. It must be one of the supported Azure locations.

createdBy.Description: The identity that created the resource.

createdByType.Description: The type of identity that created the resource. Possible values include: 'User', 'Application', 'ManagedIdentity', 'Key'

lastModifiedBy.Description: The identity that last modified the resource.

lastModifiedByType.Description: The type of identity that last modified the resource. Possible values include: 'User', 'Application', 'ManagedIdentity', 'Key'

lastModifiedAt.Description: The timestamp of resource last modification (UTC)

versions.Description: High-level information about the versions within this Template Spec. The keys are the version names. Only populated if the $expand query parameter is set to 'versions'.

timeCreated.Description: The timestamp of when the version was created.

timeModified.Description: The timestamp of when the version was last modified.

systemData.Description: Metadata pertaining to creation and last modification of the resource.

location.Description: The location of the Template Spec Version. It must match the location of the parent Template Spec.

artifacts.Description: An array of Template Spec artifacts.

template.Description: The Azure Resource Manager template content.

path.Description: A filesystem safe relative path of the artifact.

kind.Description: Represents a Template Spec artifact containing an embedded Azure Resource Manager template.
